Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我到底還能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了改變那如狹隘庭園般的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還活不到人生的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗 相擁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無意識中被刻上的經驗紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當站在懸崖邊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦難抓住了我的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往更加寬廣的領域\N往更深更大的某處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝著無法預測的世界前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And lt's calling me again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吻她一下，說不定她會醒過來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.36,0:01:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？ 王子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.36,0:02:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了…只想著這個睡美人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼說，\N因為她是貴重的MU族原型
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…剛才看到我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒什麼吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來那件事怎麼樣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣真的可以救他嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是個誠實的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多餘的長筒襪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候開始的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情有回答的必要嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「必要」 ？ 可我們是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.96,0:04:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是親密的朋友，也會有不想被別人插手的事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的檢查好像完全沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有通知說巴貝姆財團要派醫療組來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫療組
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是為了如月久遠的檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了久遠？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了，通知樹博士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,財團…為什麼對她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有話要說是吧，海倫娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有迷路的狗進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了向我報告這麼無聊的事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監控在根來彼方的如月久遠，發生了實際的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定覺醒的日子就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡的人總有一天是會甦醒的，海倫娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經派遣生理現象調查組去根來彼方了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好孩子，海倫娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美嶼…玲香…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「總覺得飛行編隊方式不太適合」\N你在想這些事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該去聽杜帕可的狂想曲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:09.44,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,{\an8}亭利·杜帕克：Henri Duparc(1848-1933)，法國作曲家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從到了這裡，任務完成率就明顯下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼看？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否對晨星型的裝備不滿？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:41.14,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}晨星型：正式名晨星2型，對MU用高速戰機，晨星就是金星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是問我這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們算什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支援部隊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要性能更強大…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說，我不可以和無關的人說太多話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很冷漠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的能幫上大叔我的忙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這個島上的事情我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說你不清楚這裡的事，但有個地方你還是很清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MU駐東京總督府長官，是個女人，你認識吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我住在那裡的時候，對那些政治、防衛之類的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.56,0:09:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是個普通的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…看看好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛世界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴眼鏡的傢伙是當時國防部的一佐，九鬼正義
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他旁邊的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七森小姐，久遠怎麼了？ ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會？…剛才她還睡在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然沒穿維生模塊就出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快發通知！盡快去找！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊修特利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有一個聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喚醒你自身的樂器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身體裡的…樂器？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像她沒來過神祠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久遠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:13:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她告訴我了，olin
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的事情嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事情？！你找到了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是olin
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1出現區域確定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它顯示在屏幕上！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,alpha小隊，DEFCON2狀態待命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon還沒準備好？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在召回機師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人，在哪裡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我必須走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.57,0:13:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早點回病房去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家會為你擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要擅自亂跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道久遠跑哪裡了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？不過剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,alpha小隊各機，緊急起飛！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標為出現在沖之鳥島西方200公里海面上的D-1
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:22.77,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}沖之鳥島：日本最南端的無人小島，具有很高的軍事經濟價值
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北緯20度，東經130度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,alpha一號，起飛！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具體情況隨後傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始傳送機師進入奈利亞神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只不過是一張照片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1的攻擊目標及移動情況尚不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰方式預計為遭遇戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機師明白了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon起飛確認
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久遠的情況怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在全島搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機師心率和血壓正常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1正位於這裡和由財團管理的Kalung Mutiara島的中間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:43.25,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kalung Mutiara：印尼語，珍珠項鏈\N在這個島的地下保存著黑色卵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼它會停在海面上？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把現在的氣象數據投影在屏幕上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:15:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是風嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現目標，距離15000
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它和卵相互呼喚，發生了共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然海上的風使聲音的方向發生了微小的偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但說不定它已經感應到這個島了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必害怕，海倫娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，叔父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小隊各機，Delta隊形！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有移動，沒有向我們反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會成功的，能擊落它的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:17:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務完成率可以提高嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,alpha一號，D-1的外形發生改變！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個混帳蘑菇！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼！久遠？
